• Built-in metal fasteners and eyelets secure papers in a bound format

description:

These presentation folders have a variety of retro designs. One order of this item contains 10 presentation folders, each with a unique retro design!

name: File Pocket™
description:
A pocket of premium synthetic materials. File Pockets™ are a no fuss solution to paper storage AND organization, just slip your File Pocket™ into another compatible product for instant separation of important files. 

Guaranteed compatibility with all P4P folding products!

Comes with selection of adhesive labels for greater organizational magic!

Comes with a 2-year limited warranty!

name: Manila Folder (Classic)
description:
Our classic folder, made of premium manila paper, has been a staple of all file storage solutions since our establishment in 1998. The sturdy stock will resist wear and tear for years. Experience the Award Winning paper file storage solution now! Comes in sets of 3. Features:
  • Capacity of up to 173 pieces of paper!
  • True manila stock in a variety of colours
  • 1/3 cut tabs for labeling purposes
